title: We are the SAME Fat with Joe DeRosa | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 36
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


Sal's on vacation so Chris is joined by the lovely Joe DeRosa! STRAP IN BABES!
